# Applied to all routes on the demo site (Cloudflare Pages).
#
# ⚠️ These headers are NOT required by the extraction library.
# Neither OPFS SyncAccessHandle, WebCodecs, nor web-demuxer use
# SharedArrayBuffer — there is no cross-origin isolation requirement.
# The library handles WASM loading via data: URL injection to bypass
# CORS entirely (see fast-extractor.ts, WASM INJECTION STRATEGY).
#
# These are set here defensively for the demo site only.
# Library consumers should NOT blindly copy these — COOP: same-origin
# breaks third-party scripts (analytics, OAuth popups, payment iframes).
/*
  Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy: credentialless
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
  Cross-Origin-Resource-Policy: cross-origin
  Access-Control-Allow-Origin: *
